# Legacy tag URL redirects.
# The old tag taxonomy used percent-encoded spaces and generic, AI-flavored
# tag names. The current taxonomy uses curated, hyphenated, named-entity
# slugs. Each old URL below 301s to the closest editorial match.
#
# Cloudflare Pages applies these rules at the edge before serving static
# assets. Source paths use percent-encoded form so they match the URLs
# search engines actually crawled. Trailing-slash variants are included
# so we never return a bare 404 to an indexed link.

